sequenceDiagram
  participant Gov as 治理层
  participant Tool as 工具层
  participant Infra as 基础设施
  participant Sandbox as 租户沙箱
  participant Audit as 审计存储
  Gov->>Tool: 授权决定 + 动作摘要 + tenant
  Tool->>Infra: 规范化执行请求 + deadline
  Infra->>Sandbox: 创建隔离环境与资源/网络边界
  Infra->>Sandbox: 注入短期 secret lease
  Sandbox->>Sandbox: 执行并限制文件、进程、网络、配额
  Sandbox-->>Infra: 结果 / artifact / effect receipt
  Infra->>Audit: image/policy/tenant/usage/结果证据
  Infra->>Sandbox: 撤销凭据、终止进程树、销毁并查残留
  Infra-->>Tool: 规范化结果或 unknown
